show.description: Ethan finds secret photos of his girlfriend Nancy with her old flame, Mark. Heartbroken, he leaves her and agrees to take over his family business abroad. But Nancy, unaware he knows, keeps getting close to Mark—right in front of him. Would you like a tagline added for extra impact?
